package Notify

All documentation, as well as the COPYING terms, is maintained within POD
documentation in the modules themselves. To see the documentation, please
use perldoc:

    perldoc Notify

Otherwise, if you have any questions or comments, send an email my way
(mgilfix@eecs.tufts.edu).

Installation
============

To install these modules, use:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

You can also install the latest version via CPAN with:

  perl -MCPAN -e'install Notify'

